rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Shoppers from all over Alst
come to Avaritia to buy all
sorts of goods, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0002
rows.name:
But that's not all who
come to Avaritia, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0003
rows.name:
There are also bad people who
steal from shoppers while they're
engrossed in their goods, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Be careful not to have things
stolen from inside your bag, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300011_04_msg0005
rows.name:
If you see a suspicious person,
report them to Rimurimu, mo.
